import asyncio
import datetime

from seed import AsyncSeedApi, NestedUser, User

client = AsyncSeedApi(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.search(
        limit=1,
        id="id",
        date=datetime.date.fromisoformat(
            "2023-01-15",
        ),
        deadline=datetime.datetime.fromisoformat(
            "2024-01-15 09:30:00+00:00",
        ),
        bytes="bytes",
        user=User(
            name="name",
            tags=["tags", "tags"],
        ),
        user_list=User(
            name="name",
            tags=["tags", "tags"],
        ),
        optional_deadline=datetime.datetime.fromisoformat(
            "2024-01-15 09:30:00+00:00",
        ),
        key_value={"keyValue": "keyValue"},
        optional_string="optionalString",
        nested_user=NestedUser(
            name="name",
            user=User(
                name="name",
                tags=["tags", "tags"],
            ),
        ),
        optional_user=User(
            name="name",
            tags=["tags", "tags"],
        ),
        exclude_user=User(
            name="name",
            tags=["tags", "tags"],
        ),
        filter="filter",
        neighbor=User(
            name="name",
            tags=["tags", "tags"],
        ),
        neighbor_required=User(
            name="name",
            tags=["tags", "tags"],
        ),
    )


asyncio.run(main())
